&lt;p&gt;The Detroit Lions are building something special and we want the right person in the room when it matters most. We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Director of Corporate Partnership Sales&lt;/strong&gt; to lead the charge in growing our corporate partnerships portfolio. This isn&#39;t just a sales role — it&#39;s a chance to shape the commercial future of one of the NFL&#39;s most storied franchises.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
